{{> layout/header}}

<style>
    .page-title {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 20px;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
</style>

<div class="container p-5">

    <div class="page-title">
        <h1>평가지</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="card mb-3">
        <div class="card-header">
            <div>
                시험일 : {{model.evaluationDate}} <br>
                시험장소 : {{model.loc}} <br>
                교과목 : {{model.subjectTitle}} <br>
                훈련교사 : {{model.teacherName}} <br>
                문항수 : {{model.questionCount}} <br>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div style="border: 2px solid #ced4da; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; background-color: #f8f9fa;"
         class="mb-3">
        <p style="margin-bottom: 8px;">
            <strong>🔗 상세 예시 링크:</strong>
            <a href="{{model.guideLink}}" target="_blank"
               style="color: #0d6efd; text-decoration: underline;">
                {{model.guideLink}}
            </a>
        </p>

        <div style="margin-bottom: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: #343a40;">
            이 과제의 정답은 다양할 수 있으며, 아래와 같은 수준의 결과물이 이상적입니다:
        </div>

        <ul style="padding-left: 20px; line-height: 1.6; color: #495057; margin: 0;">
            {{#model.guideSummaries}}
                <li>{{.}}</li>
            {{/model.guideSummaries}}
        </ul>
    </div>

    {{#model.questions}}
        <div class="card mb-4">
            <div class="card-header fw-bold">
                {{no}}. {{title}} <!-- 문제 제목 -->
            </div>

            <div class="card-body p-3">
                <table class="table table-bordered">
                    <thead class="table-light">
                    <tr>
                        <th style="width: 80px;" class="text-center">점수</th>
                        <th>평가기준 (루브릭 설명)</th>
                    </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                    {{#options}}
                        <tr>
                            <td class="text-center fw-bold align-middle">{{point}}점</td>
                            <td>{{rubricItem}}</td>
                        </tr>
                    {{/options}}
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
        </div>
    {{/model.questions}}
</div>

{{> layout/footer}}